{"id":"322161226_Visual_languages_A_graphical_review","abstract":"We present a graphical review of the research on visual languages in the last 20 years. In particular, we gathered and analyzed the data about a set of publications in the field from 1995 to 2014. Visual techniques employed include graph-based visualization such as collaboration, co-citation, and co-word networks. We also adopted geographical views, alluvial diagrams, and timelined charts. The produced charts allowed us to have a deeper knowledge on the field of visual languages and on the scientific community working on it.","authors":["Gennaro Costagliola","Mattia De Rosa","Vittorio Fuccella","Stefano Perna"],"meta":["July 2017Information Visualization 17(4):147387161771452","DOI:10.1177/1473871617714520"],"references":["271021532_Visualizing_information_science_Author_direct_citation_analysis_in_China_and_around_the_world","268449133_Synthetic_Biology_Open_Language_Visual_SBOL_Visual_version_10_0","265372476_Pathfinder_Associative_Networks_Studies_in_Knowledge_Organization","262977655_ForceAtlas2_a_Continuous_Graph_Layout_Algorithm_for_Handy_Network_Visualization_Designed_for_the_Gephi_Software","259288466_LeeMR_and_TT_Chen_2012Revealing_research_themes_and_trends_in_knowledge_management_From_1995_to_2010_Knowledge-Based_SystemsVolume_28_April_2012_Pages_47-58","243772975_String_Comparator_Metrics_and_Enhanced_Decision_Rules_in_the_Fellegi-Sunter_Model_of_Record_Linkage","227655644_Co-Citation_in_the_Scientific_Literature_A_New_Measure_of_the_Relationship_Between_Two_Documents","223978080_Mapping_the_Knowledge_Structure_of_Research_on_Patient_Adherence_Knowledge_Domain_Visualization_Based_Co-Word_Analysis_and_Social_Network_Analysis","221517792_An_Organic_User_Interface_for_Searching_Citatino_Links","220586688_CiteWiz_A_Tool_for_the_Visualization_of_Scientific_Citation_Networks","220434125_Time_line_visualization_of_research_fronts","220432711_Visualizing_Science_by_Citation_Mapping","220426817_Scr